Entegrion, Inc. Key Developments

Entegrion, Inc. Wins $27.76 Million Federal Contract
Sep 24 16
Entegrion Inc. was awarded a $27,761,899 federal contract set aside for small business by the U.S. Army Medical Research for clinical trial of a pooled, spray dried solvent detergent plasma product for the treatment of patients with significant hemorrhaging. The place of performance will be in Durham, North Carolina.


