Our Products





Entegrion’s products seek to fill unmet market needs.

Our plasma and platelet technologies bridge a gap in current blood banking technology that dates back more than half a century.
Our PCM will provide data faster to doctors and directly to first responders, accelerating life-saving therapies.

Building from these unique technologies provides us with a significant platform for expansion.

Our Resusix™ and Stasix® technologies are the foundation of our hemostatic patch.
And our Stasix® particles can be loaded with imaging and highly cytotoxic materials for targeted delivery to areas of vascular distress.

